rows.label: qst660109_msg0001
rows.name: We need to go back to Alst now.

rows.label: qst660109_msg0003
rows.name:
It doesn't look like we can go with you,
so we'll just wait for you here.

rows.label: qst660109_msg0006
rows.name:
We'll be back soon enough I'm sure.
Keep yourselves occupied, yeah?

rows.label: qst660109_msg0007
rows.name: Will do, Rex. Get back safe.

rows.label: qst660109_msg0008
rows.name:
It shouldn't be too long.
When we return, I'm sure we'll
have need of all three of you!
